AGC Player解锁会员 = type=http-response, pattern=https://api.agcplayer.com/, script-path=https://raw.githubusercontent.com/BOBOLAOSHIV587/Rules/main/JS/AGC/JS/AGC.js, requires-body=true, max-size=-1, timeout=60


